he weekend falling on March 28-29, so the last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday). Since today is only March 30 (Monday), I should respond that today isn't the last working day.\\n\\nThe truncated message at the end likely contains additional instructions for what to do when it is the last working day, but I can't see those details. For now, I'll follow the clear part of the instruction and send the response about today not being the last working day.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**本月最后工作日不是今天，不执行**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**原因**：2026年3月工作日分析：\\n- 3月28日（周六）、3月29日（周日）→ 周末休息\\n- **本月最后工作日为3月31日（周二）**\\n- 今天是3月30日（周一），非本月最后工作日\\n\\n待3月31日再来执行本月日报汇总评价和打分。🦞\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774802419715\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:05e9f9b7-5879-4a26-8345-3d4d0563a347\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本…\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本…\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774802303001,\n      \"sessionId\": \"32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44170,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me think about this. The user is asking me to:\\n1. Check if today (March 30, 2026) is the last working day of this quarter\\n2. If yes, execute the quarterly daily report summary evaluation and scoring workflow\\n3. If no, reply with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\"\\n\\nFirst, let me determine what quarter today falls into:\\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday\\n- Q1 = January, February, March (ending March 31)\\n- Today is March 30, which is the second-to-last day of Q1\\n\\nIs March 30, 2026 a working day? Let me check the calendar:\\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday - this is a working day\\n- March 31, 2026 is a Tuesday - this is also a working day\\n\\nSo today (March 30) is NOT the last working day of Q1. The last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday).\\n\\nWait, I need to check if March 31 is a public holiday in China. Let me think... \\n\\nActually, I should just follow the instructions as given. Today is March 30, 2026 (Monday), which is NOT the last working day of Q1 (March 31 would be). So I should reply with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\".\\n\\nBut wait - this is a cron job asking me to perform the quarterly summary. The instructions say \\\"首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复'本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行'\\\"\\n\\n\\nSince today is indeed March 30, and the last working day of Q1 is March 31, today is not the last working day. I should respond with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\".\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"<final>本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774802405045\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":10,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775058229543,"sessionId":"fed4146b-932d-4d92-9a5d-df75c9609f57","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45573,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/fed4146b-932d-4d92-9a5d-df75c9609f57.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. There are no recent user messages (within 5 minutes) from other sessions. This cron job is running in an isolated session and its only message is from this cron run itself.\n\nLet me check if there are any other sessions - I should look at the main session specifically. Let me check sessions more broadly to see if there's a main user session.\n\nActually, looking at the result, the only session is \"agent:main:cron:...\" which is this cron job itself. The \"last message\" shown is the cron job's own assistant message. This means there are no active user conversations.\n\nHowever, I need to be careful - this could be the cron job checking itself. Let me look for sessions with kind \"user\" or sessions from the feishu channel. Let me try to list all sessions without the activeMinutes filter.\n\nWait - the session key is \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2...\" which indicates this is a cron-triggered isolated session. The `updatedAt` timestamp shows this session was just active. But the question is whether there are other user sessions.\n\nLet me check if there are any sessions from the feishu channel (which would indicate real user conversations).\n\nActually, the sessions_list with `activeMinutes: 5` and `messageLimit: 1` should show sessions active within 5 minutes. The only result is this cron job session. But I need to check if there might be a main session with姚总 that's active.\n\nLet me try a broader search - looking at all sessions without the activeMinutes filter."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x2x3ro1cu6my_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":10,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775058234965}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:89062ef1-aea1-4ec1-aa22-e28c8a2c3bf1","kind":"other","channel":"feishu","displayName":"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-89062ef1-aea1-4ec1-aa22-e28c8a2c3bf1","deliveryContext":{"channel":"feishu"},"updatedAt":1775057804789,"sessionId":"d857f2f0-a273-4a1b-b972-0512e54ac3e9","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":48333,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"feishu","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/d857f2f0-a273-4a1b-b972-0512e54ac3e9.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully searched for the latest industry trends across all 4 directions and saved them to the file. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n✅ **任务完成** — 已搜索4个方向的2026年行业最新动态并保存到 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**搜索方向与核心发现：**\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：AI多智能体（70%企业已部署）+垂直大模型成核心引擎；政策面上\"十五五\"规划与中小企业数字化专项行动方案同步推进\n\n2. **智能安防/弱电工程**：AIoT从\"被动响应\"升级为\"主动预判\"；数字孪生普及率超60%；行业从硬件销售转向服务能力驱动\n\n3. **网络系统集成/算力网络**：工信部\"1+M+N\"全国算力互联互通节点体系正式落地；全光交换商用化；国产AI芯片渗透率升至39%\n\n4. **IT运维/AIOps**：65%中大型企业已部署AIOps生产环境；LLMOps融合加速；AIOps 3.0全自治运维体系成为发展方向\n\n**文件包含：** 5条关键信息，每条含标题、日期（2026年）、具体摘要内容，已加标签分类。\n\n**文件路径：** `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775057796709}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:6d471548-5571-47e4-9495-d8e1378c7fdb","kind":"other","channel":"feishu","displayName":"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-6d471548-5571-47e4-9495-d8e1378c7fdb","deliveryContext":{"channel":"feishu"},"updatedAt":1775057420381,"sessionId":"2cc754b1-faa7-49fc-9825-0fd4a7b81961","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45119,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"feishu","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/2cc754b1-faa7-49fc-9825-0fd4a7b81961.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have the search results from three different queries. Let me compile a comprehensive summary of 3-5 key pieces of information covering all the relevant industries for 道简网络 (enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, IT operation services).\n\nLet me organize the key findings into a concise summary:\n\n1. **企业数字化转型政策** - 2026年国家政策密集发布，包括200亿专项资金支持中小企业数字化转型，汽车行业专项方案，工业数据筑基行动等\n2. **智能安防行业** - AI大模型和智能体成为核心技术，中国市场年复合增长率15.1%，头部企业生态整合加速\n\n\n3. **网络系统集成与IT运维** - 算力网络升级和AIOps智能运维正在重塑行业格局，云原生与信创国产化成为关键方向\n\nThese three insights capture the most important trends affecting 道简网络's core business areas."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n## 道简网络相关行业最新动态摘要（2026年4月）\n\n---\n\n### 一、企业数字化转型：政策密集落地，200亿专项扶持中小企业\n\n2026年国家层面政策呈多维度推进态势。核心动态：国家推出\"中小企业数字化转型加速计划（2026-2028）\"，设立**200亿元专项资金**，对采购云服务、智能设备的中小企业给予最高30%购置补贴；制造业研发费用加计扣除比例提升至120%。工信部同步启动\"工业数据筑基行动\"，目标2026年底实现工业数据资源汇聚与高质量数据集建设。工业互联网与AI融合加速，明确到2028年融合赋能目标。\n\n**地方层面**：北京市出台新政鼓励数字化转型，最高支持500万元；广东省目标2026年底推动超4000家规上工业企业开展数字化转型。政策趋势从通用支持转向行业专项与区域特色相结合，精准解决企业\"不敢转、不会转、不想转\"痛点。\n\n---\n\n### 二、智能安防：AI大模型驱动行业升维，中国市场增速领先全球\n\n智能安防全球市场规模预计达1500-2000亿美元，中国作为全球最大市场占全球份额35%，年复合增长率达**15.1%**，增速领先全球。核心技术方向：AI大模型、AI智能体、具身智能机器人成为技术核心，推动安防从\"被动监控\"向\"主动感知-智能判断-主动处置\"全链路闭环演进。头部企业如海康威视、华为等通过AI算法+云计算构建生态壁垒。行业挑战方面，数据安全合规要求趋严（数据安全法、个人信息保护法），不同品牌设备间\"数据孤岛\"问题亟待整合。\n\n---\n\n### 三、网络系统集成：从\"连接通道\"向\"算力调度基础设施\"升级\n\n网络功能从传统数据传输向算力资源动态调度演进。典型案例：中国移动\"算力网络试验网\"已在12个省份部署，通过SRv6+APN6技术实现AI训练任务跨数据中心自动调度，端到端时延波动控制在±0.5毫秒内。这意味着网络系统集成商的角色正在从基础设施施工向\"算力调度+智能化网络服务\"升级，对交付能力提出更高要求。\n\n---\n\n### 四、IT运维服务：AIOps智能化重构行业，成本与ESG成新焦点\n\n智能化运维（AIOps）深度落地，AI Agent替代脚本化自动化，实现故障预测与智能决策，推动\"被动监控\"向\"主动治理\"转变。云原生架构（Kubernetes、Serverless）成为标准底座，运维从\"劳动密集型\"转向\"知识密集型\"。国产化替代加速，信创适配与合规能力成核心竞争力。同时，成本节约与可持续性纳入ESG考核，运维服务需提升资源利用效率。行业痛点明显：传统\"救火式\"被动运维占比仍高，AIOps能力与自动化异常处理能力显著不足，亟需升级。\n\n---\n\n**小结**：2026年行业整体呈现\"政策强力推动+AI技术深度渗透+国产化加速\"三重趋势，道简网络主营的企业数字化、智能安防、系统集成、IT运维四大业务板块均处于政策红利与技术升级的双重机遇期，建议持续关注数字化转型专项资金申报、AI+安防产品集成、算力网络服务能力建设等方向。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775057393579}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:d0fd6a2f-f302-4007-874b-0df8159f7a91","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","displayName":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","updatedAt":1775016114081,"sessionId":"10a79e90-d2aa-4c3b-b827-9800b4574ea6","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":64723,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/10a79e90-d2aa-4c3b-b827-9800b4574ea6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have completed the daily reflection. Let me summarize the key lessons learned today:\n\n1. **教训23 - 超满分错误**：刘晓点评计算出103分，超过满分100分。这是一个低级错误，说明我在发送前没有完整检查所有数字。\n\n2. **教训24 - 归档询问错误**：发送完日报点评确认版后，我两次问姚总\"请回复'发送'\"，这违反了\"归档是刚性流程，不能问\"的原则。姚总明确说\"我都说了不要问，直接归档\"。\n\n根因分析：\n- 教训24的根因是我没有深度理解姚总\"直接发\"的含义\n- 姚总说\"直接发\"应该理解为：准备内容 → 直接发员工 → 直接归档，三位一体，不需要任何询问\n- 我用\"询问\"代替了\"执行\"，这是惰性思维\n\n我已经将这些教训更新到了 lessons.md 和 2026-04-01.md 中。"},{"type":"text","text":"## 每日复盘反思\n\n### 今日教训\n\n**教训23 - 刘晓点评超满分计算错误（🟠严重）**\n- 非销售评分计算：计划完成度30+经验沉淀15+计划质量10+汇报质量48=**103分**\n- 超过满分100分，发送确认版后才主动承认\n\n**根因**：没有在发送前检查总分是否超过满分，自我检查机制缺失\n\n**教训24 - 归档3步法是刚性流程，不能询问（🔴致命）**\n- 发送完7位员工确认版后，两次问\"请回复'发送'\"\n- 姚总回复**\"我都说了不要问，直接归档\"**\n\n**深度根因**：\n1. 姚总早上说\"直接发\"，我理解为\"不需确认直接发给员工\"，但仍认为需要问\"是否继续归档\"\n2. **没有理解\"直接发\"的完整含义**：= 准备内容 → 直接发员工 → 直接归档，三位一体\n3. **用\"询问\"代替\"执行\"，这是惰性思维**\n\n### 固化要求\n\n| 要求 | 具体 |\n|------|------|\n| 超满分检查 | 评分计算完成后必须验证：总分 ≤ 100分（非销售） |\n| 归档不问 | 绝不能再问\"是否归档\"、\"请回复'发送'\" |\n| 姚总说\"直接\" | = 直接发员工 + 直接归档，不需要任何确认 |\n| 归档自动执行 | 无论哪种路径，**归档都是自动执行**，不需要问 |\n\n### 待补救\n\n⚠️ **2026-03-30日报点评归档仍未完成**：\n- 知识库文档只有王文强、王垣皓，缺5位员工\n- 必须尽快补救\n\n---\n\n教训已固化到 `memory/lessons.md`，日志已更新至 `memory/2026-04-01.md`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775016359163}]},{"key":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","kind":"other","channel":"feishu","displayName":"姚霖","deliveryContext":{"channel":"feishu","to":"user:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1775014662414,"sessionId":"df70408b-c83e-4787-bbbb-44560e019b0c","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":129974,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"feishu","lastTo":"user:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/df70408b-c83e-4787-bbbb-44560e019b0c.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能文件已更新并同步到知识库。"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成 ✅\n\n**教训总结（已写入技能文件）：**\n\n| 教训 | 核心要求 |\n|------|----------|\n| **教训1** | 归档是刚性流程，发送完员工后**立即执行，不问** |\n| **教训2** | 姚总说\"直接\"就**直接执行**，不多此一举 |\n| **教训3** | **一次性**执行完整套流程，最后只汇报\"已完成\" |\n| **教训4** | 根据姚总措辞判断路径：说\"直接发\"→直接发；说\"先确认\"→先发确认版 |\n\n技能文件已同步至本地+知识库。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775014656620}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:c42d0c3d-fe26-49b7-977d-adb6ad322857","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行昨日日报点评","displayName":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行昨日日报点评","updatedAt":1775005883061,"sessionId":"1ce56efb-bb2a-4185-9150-6535406e6a6e","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":82715,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/1ce56efb-bb2a-4185-9150-6535406e6a6e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，所有7位员工的日报点评确认版都已发送完毕。现在等待姚总回复\"发送\"后再发送员工版，然后进行归档。让我先整理一下已发送的日报点评汇总：\n\n| 员工 | 总分 | 等级 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 王文强 | 84分 | B |\n| 王垣皓 | 61分 | D |\n| 胡文正 | 83分 | B |\n| 刘世龙 | 70分 | C |\n| 李文娅 | 91分 | A |\n| 郝彦艳 | 65分 | D |\n| 刘晓 | 103分（满分100封顶）→ 实际100分 | A |\n\n等等，刘晓的分数我写的是103分，这不对，满分是100分。让我重新算一下：\n- 计划完成度：30分\n- 经验沉淀：15分\n- 计划质量：10分\n- 汇报质量：48分\n总计：30+15+10+48 = 103分，但满分100分封顶，所以应该是100分。\n\n不过我写的是103分，这是一个错误。但已经发出去了，需要等姚总确认时说明。\n\n现在等待姚总回复\"发送\"，然后执行归档流程。"},{"type":"text","text":"7位员工的日报点评确认版已全部发送完毕。\n\n**日报点评汇总（3月31日）：**\n\n| 员工 | 部门 | 职务 | 总分 | 等级 |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| 王文强 | 销售部 | 销售 | 84分 | B |\n| 王垣皓 | 销售部 | 销售 | 61分 | D |\n| 胡文正 | 运维部 | 运维工程师 | 83分 | B |\n| 刘世龙 | 运维部 | 运维工程师 | 70分 | C |\n| 李文娅 | 商务部 | 商务 | 91分 | A |\n| 郝彦艳 | 商务部 | 商务 | 65分 | D |\n| 刘晓 | 商务部 | 商务 | 100分 | A |\n\n**待姚总确认后发送员工版并进行归档。**\n\n---\n⚠️ **刘晓点评中存在分数计算错误**：我计算了103分，但满分100分封顶，实际应为100分（A级）。发送时未检查满分上限，恳请姚总在确认时知悉修正。\n\n请回复\"发送\"以继续员工版发送流程，或告知需要修改的点评。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775006283169}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:cfd2966c-5e50-4153-ac26-a51b644dbe4a","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 每日AI科技早报","displayName":"Cron: 每日AI科技早报","updatedAt":1775005405815,"sessionId":"4817daba-3eb8-4220-8480-03cd969d16f6","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45932,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/4817daba-3eb8-4220-8480-03cd969d16f6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the news. Let me compile this into a clear morning briefing. The task asks me to send it to the user, but this is a cron job that should auto-deliver. Let me look at the cron payload to understand what the task expects.\n\nThe cron job description says \"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\" So I should just return the summary as plain text.\n\nLet me format the briefing nicely."},{"type":"text","text":"**🦞 AI科技早报 · 2026.04.01**\n\n---\n\n**1. DeepSeek V4 正式发布**\n国产大模型 DeepSeek V4 确认4月上线，采用\"万亿参数+原生多模态\"架构，支持文本/图片/视频联合理解生成。已完成华为昇腾、寒武纪等国产芯片深度适配，1M Token上下文时延压至600ms，优于H100版本。代码能力大幅强化，可一次性处理30万行代码逻辑链。\n\n**2. OpenAI 打造\"统一超级应用\"**\nOpenAI 正在整合 ChatGPT、Codex、浏览器及智能体功能，打造跨场景协同的超级应用。GPT-4o、GPT-4.1、GPT-5 等老模型已于2月在 ChatGPT 下线，仅 Business 付费用户可使用至4月。\n\n**3. 微软 Copilot 集成 Claude**\n微软推出\"Frontier Program\"，Copilot 新增\"Critique 功能\"——GPT 起草+Claude 校对，专门优化长任务处理能力。\n\n**4. 苹果 AI 生态加速布局**\niOS 26.4 支持 CarPlay 使用 AI 聊天机器人；iOS 27 将推出第三方 Siri Extensions，并酝酿\"AI App Store\"开放生态。\n\n**5. 智能体成行业新赛道**\n行业判断\"推理军备竞赛\"边际收益递减，以 OpenAI o1、DeepSeek R1 为代表的\"延长推理链\"路线接近瓶颈。下一阶段竞争核心转向**智能体（Agent）**——强调自主任务规划与多工具协同能力。\n\n**6. 4月国产模型密集发布**\nDeepSeek V4 与腾讯混元新模型预计同期上线，国内大模型赛道进入新一轮技术竞速。\n\n**7. DeepSeek 发布前现服务波动**\n3月29日至31日 DeepSeek 服务连续三天异常，故障累计超13小时，或与新模型上线前压力测试有关。\n\n---\n\n*以上信息综合自公开报道，具体以官方为准*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775005439530}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee141b","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 服务状态巡检","displayName":"Cron: 服务状态巡检","updatedAt":1774839690835,"sessionId":"1fd238c8-fdc9-4074-97c9-167a06946059","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44995,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/1fd238c8-fdc9-4074-97c9-167a06946059.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1774839691364,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:215b7619-c198-4ed9-89bf-88e6c89cfee6","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本月的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\"本月最…","displayName":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本月的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\"本月最…","updatedAt":1774802419324,"sessionId":"3ad57bdd-1755-4a92-8ae0-a60f8c3c6e08","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44166,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/3ad57bdd-1755-4a92-8ae0-a60f8c3c6e08.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the AGENTS.md to understand the workflow for monthly summary.\n\nWait, this is a cron job asking me to determine if today is the last working day of the month. But the message got cut off. Let me re-read it.\n\nThe message says: \"请按照日报点评工作流执行本月的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复'本月最…'\"\n\nThe message got truncated. But I can see the full instruction: \"首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复'本月最后工作日不是今天，不执行'\"\n\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 12:40 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-29 16:40 UTC\n\n\nSince the message is in Chinese and instructs me to reply with \"本月最后工作日不是今天，不执行\" if today isn't the last working day, I need to determine whether March 30, 2026 is actually the final working day of the month in China.\n\nMarch 2026 has 31 days, with the weekend falling on March 28-29, so the last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday). Since today is only March 30 (Monday), I should respond that today isn't the last working day.\n\nThe truncated message at the end likely contains additional instructions for what to do when it is the last working day, but I can't see those details. For now, I'll follow the clear part of the instruction and send the response about today not being the last working day."},{"type":"text","text":"**本月最后工作日不是今天，不执行**\n\n---\n\n**原因**：2026年3月工作日分析：\n- 3月28日（周六）、3月29日（周日）→ 周末休息\n- **本月最后工作日为3月31日（周二）**\n- 今天是3月30日（周一），非本月最后工作日\n\n待3月31日再来执行本月日报汇总评价和打分。🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774802419715}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:05e9f9b7-5879-4a26-8345-3d4d0563a347","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\"本…","displayName":"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\"本…","updatedAt":1774802303001,"sessionId":"32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44170,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me think about this. The user is asking me to:\n1. Check if today (March 30, 2026) is the last working day of this quarter\n2. If yes, execute the quarterly daily report summary evaluation and scoring workflow\n3. If no, reply with \"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\"\n\nFirst, let me determine what quarter today falls into:\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday\n- Q1 = January, February, March (ending March 31)\n- Today is March 30, which is the second-to-last day of Q1\n\nIs March 30, 2026 a working day? Let me check the calendar:\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday - this is a working day\n- March 31, 2026 is a Tuesday - this is also a working day\n\nSo today (March 30) is NOT the last working day of Q1. The last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday).\n\nWait, I need to check if March 31 is a public holiday in China. Let me think... \n\nActually, I should just follow the instructions as given. Today is March 30, 2026 (Monday), which is NOT the last working day of Q1 (March 31 would be). So I should reply with \"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\".\n\nBut wait - this is a cron job asking me to perform the quarterly summary. The instructions say \"首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复'本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行'\"\n\n\nSince today is indeed March 30, and the last working day of Q1 is March 31, today is not the last working day. I should respond with \"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\"."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774802405045}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775058246431}}
{"type":"message","id":"099c654e","parentId":"d90caced","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:44:27.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the sessions list carefully:\n\n1. **This cron job session** (agent:main:cron:3709e1d2...) - updatedAt: 1775058229543 (just now, this current session)\n2. **feishu subagent session** (89062ef1...) - updatedAt: 1775057804789 (about 7 minutes ago) - channel: feishu\n3. **feishu subagent session** (6d471548...) - updatedAt: 1775057420381 (about 13 minutes ago) - channel: feishu  \n4. **Daily review cron** (d0fd6a2f...) - updatedAt: 1775016114081 (about 11 hours ago)\n5. **姚霖 direct session** (feishu:direct:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) - updatedAt: 1775014662414 (about 12 hours ago)\n\n\n6. **Daily report review cron** (c42d0c3d...) - updatedAt: 1775005883061 (about 14 hours ago)\n7. **AI news cron** (cfd2966c...) - updatedAt: 1775005405815 (about 14 hours ago)\n8. **Service health check cron** (99dd3c6e...) - updatedAt: 1774839690835 (about 2 days ago)\n9. **Monthly summary cron** (215b7619...) - updatedAt: 1774802419324 (about 3 days ago)\n\nThe feishu subagent sessions are the most recent active sessions, particularly the two from about 7-13 minutes ago that were running feishu tasks.\n\nLooking at the activeMinutes: 5 filter - those feishu subagents were active around 1775057804789 and 1775057420381, which puts them at roughly 7-14 minutes old. The current time is 1775058235037, so these sessions fall outside the 5-minute window and wouldn't be considered active by that filter.\n\nHowever, the cron job's own session was just updated at 1775058229543, which is basically now. The task is asking whether there are any user conversations happening right now - I need to check if there's actually a user message in the main feishu:direct session or if these are just background cron processes running. The feishu subagents haven't had user messages recently - their most recent activity was around 13 minutes ago. The cron sessions show system-sent messages but no actual user interactions. So it looks like the main conversation with 姚总 hasn't received any recent messages, which means I should go ahead with the autonomous learning task. There's a mismatch between the current timestamp (1775058235037 in milliseconds) and the stated time of \"Wednesday, April 1st 2026 — 11:43 PM\", which is only about 11 minutes after the last activity. I need to verify whether these feishu subagents actually represent active user conversations or just automated cron processes that ran earlier. Given the timestamp discrepancy and the nature of the sessions, I should proceed with the autonomous learning task as requested. The feishu subagents show very recent activity around 7-14 minutes ago, but they're isolated agents spawned for specific tasks rather than direct user conversations. The actual user session with 姚总 hasn't had activity in over 12 hours. Given the 5-minute threshold means there are no actively engaged user conversations right now, I should proceed with the autonomous learning task as instructed.","thinkingSignature":"733cf1ba3c53b18b527985906794b4c70f35b0f6035b3cf508687bb2d1e2862a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s6m0z8qttseo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9047,"output":801,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53829,"cost":{"input":0.0027140999999999997,"output":0.0009611999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004994729999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775058246435}}
{"type":"message","id":"088a253f","parentId":"099c654e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:44:27.860Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s6m0z8qttseo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775058267855}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1938d59","parentId":"088a253f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:44:34.560Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll perform 4 web searches simultaneously to gather industry information for 道简网络's related industries.","thinkingSignature":"dfdab87b3d3a0eddb27d3e8dfc75a3b88e29667095bff3806995956cfb23e302"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c73rnsx7f1gl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c73rnsx7f1gl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 AI大模型 2026最新动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c73rnsx7f1gl_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 算力网络 2026最新动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c73rnsx7f1gl_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 AIOps 智能化运维 2026最新动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10363,"output":268,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54612,"cost":{"input":0.0031089,"output":0.0003216,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004749929999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775058267859}}
